    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sovereign states typically originating with a large group of people associated with a particular territory and possessing distinct ethnic, historical, or cultural characteristics.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
